***1_Feature file with Scenario***
Feature − Payment Process
Scenario − Credit card transaction
    Given user is on credit card payment screen
    Then user should be able to complete credit card payment

***1_Implementation file(in Python)***
from behave import *
@given('user is on credit card payment screen')
def impl(context):
    print('check due amount if any')
@then('user should be able to complete credit card payment')
def impl(context):
    print('successful transaction')

***2_Feature file with Scenario Outline***
Feature − User information
Scenario Outline - Check login functionality
    Given user enters <name> and <password>
    Then user should be logged in
    Examples: Credentials
        | name  | password |
        | user1 | pwd1     |
        | user2 | pwd2     |

***2_Implementation file(in Python)***
from behave import *
@given('user enters "{name}" and "{password}"')
def step_impl(context, name, password):
    print("Username for login: {}".format(name))
        print("Password for login: {}".format(password))
@then('user should be logged in')
def step_impl(context):
    pass